The '''Business Architects Association''' [http://www.businessarchitects.org] is the international governing body for the Business Architect's field. Its mission is to "Promote and advance the Business Architect field through education, research, community involvement, and application of methodologies for the benefit of the business community at large." The BAA confers the Certified Business Architect ("CBA") certification.